Package cs2030s.fp

Class Lazy<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030s.fp.Lazy<T>
  • public class Lazy<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper around a Maybe object that might contain an item or might not. Does not evaluate the Producer until called upon.

        public <U> Lazy<U> flatMap​(cs2030s.fp.Transformer<? super T,​? extends Lazy<? extends U>> t)
        Maps the current value to a new value using a Transformer. The function is stored as a producer and is only evaluated when called by get(). Instead of returning a value wrapped around twice, returns the producer wrapped only once.
